Constraintbox widget -> to set min and max height of textview to be set. Textview should be set
within this widget.

animatedwidget, animated positioned or animatinig padding -> can be used in animation

AnimatedSwitcher to switch (transition) between two Widgets...

AnimatedBuilder to add animation to any widget. (wrap your code in build function and in state widget)

User Flex Widget for weight instead.


AnimatedList for list animation (insert update delete)

ValueNotifier : to get an update or changes from any widget and udpate the widget automatically
when value updated. (ValuelistenableBuilder). Use with InheritableWidgets to access throughout your
widget tree.

Transform widget for animation